Today I solved the following LeetCode problem in C++:

## âœ… 507. Perfect Number  
**Problem Link:** [Perfect Number](https://leetcode.com/problems/perfect-number/)  
**Approach:** Checked all divisors of the number up to `num / 2` and summed them. If the sum equals the number itself, itâ€™s a perfect number.

```cpp
class Solution {
public:
    bool checkPerfectNumber(int num) {
        int sum = 0;
        for(int i = 1 ; i <= num/2 ; i++){
            if(num%i==0) sum+=i;
            if(sum > num ) return false;
        }
        return sum == num;
    }
};
```

